Some people in the world believe Israel is in the right. Others believe the 
Palestinians are in the right. (And so on...)

Even if these various factions commit crimes against the other factions, those 
who believe the actors are in the right will believe that those actors - 
particularly Israel - should not be prosecuted under laws they feel are unjust.

This is known as Jewry nullification.
